    "frontendNotes": [
      "Use semantic tokens instead of direct hex references in components.",
      "Skill IDs should use monospace; human-readable titles should use regular UI typography.",
      "Keep table row height stable even when asset counts change.",
      "Preserve filter and selected skill state when switching inspector tabs.",
      "Use the display serif only for page title and occasional brand/entity moments, not for table content.",
